OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives pledge to scrap
OL,4,Cstamp duty and deliver M4 relief road
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives have pledged
OL,7,Fto cut the basic rate of income tax by
OL,8,F1p and scrap stamp duty in Wales if
OL,9,Fthey are elected in May's Senedd
OL,10,Felection.
OL,12,FThey are the first party to publish
OL,13,Ftheir plans ahead of polling day in
OL,14,FMay.
OL,16,FUnveiling the manifesto in Cardiff
OL,17,FBay, leader Darren Millar said the
OL,18,Fparty was launching 'Fix Wales' the
OL,19,FConservative plan to 'get Wales
OL,20,Fworking'.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
