OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives pledge to scrap
OL,4,Cstamp duty and deliver M4 relief road
OL,6,F"It's a positive plan to unleash
OL,7,Feconomic growth, create jobs, promote
OL,8,Fhome ownership, cut taxes and waste,
OL,9,Fput more money into the pockets of
OL,10,Fhardworking people across the country,
OL,11,Fand fix our public services."
OL,13,FManifesto commitments include:
OL,15,FAddressing the audience at the
OL,16,Fmanifesto launch, Darren Millar said:
OL,17,F"People in Wales are crying out for
OL,18,Fpositive change, this is our credible
OL,19,Fand costed plan to deliver just that.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
