PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772701496
OL,3,CWelsh Conservatives pledge to scrap
OL,4,Cstamp duty and deliver M4 relief road
OL,6,F"Our message to the people of Wales is
OL,7,Fthis: no matter where you live, or
OL,8,Fwhat your circumstances are, you'll be
OL,9,Fbetter off under a Welsh Conservative
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,F"Labour has failed Wales. But they
OL,13,Fwouldn't have been able to do it
OL,14,Fwithout the support of Plaid and the
OL,15,FLiberal Democrats. A vote for any of
OL,16,Fthose parties, is a vote for more of
OL,17,Fthe same."
